<p>
The <b>tensor algebra</b> \(T^\bullet(V)\)
is:
\[T^\bullet(V) := \bigoplus_{k\ge 0}T^k(V)\]
where \(T^0(V) = \mathbf F,\; T^1(V) = V,\;
T^2(V) = V\otimes V,\;
T^3(V) = V\otimes V\otimes V,\;\dots\)
</p>
<p>
Here, \(\otimes\) is the
<a knowl="defs/vec/tensor-prod">tensor product</a>.
</p>
<p>
Related: <a knowl="defs/vec/alt-alg">alternating algebra</a>.
</p>
</body>
</html>
